snippet.title: Game Boy - Asmik-kun World 2 © 1991 Asmik - Gameplay
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Asmik-kun World 2 is a Puzzle game, developed by Cyclone System and published by Asmik Ace Entertainment, Inc, which was released in Japan in 1991.
